### CorpAssist Chat API（本地示例）
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = {{$dotenv CORPASSIST_TOKEN}}

### 同步对话
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "年假制度摘要",
  "conversationId": "c-demo-1"
}

### SSE 流式
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/chat/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "年假制度摘要",
  "conversationId": "c-demo-1"
}

### 校验失败（空 message）
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "",
  "conversationId": "c-demo-1"
}
